Tye Kayle Sheridan -LRB- born November 11 , 1996 -RRB- is an American actor .
Sheridan made his feature film debut in Terrence Malick 's experimental drama film The Tree of Life -LRB- 2011 -RRB- and had his first leading role in Jeff Nichols 's film Mud -LRB- 2012 -RRB- .
He also co-starred in David Gordon Green 's drama Joe -LRB- 2013 -RRB- .
In 2015 , he starred in the drama The Stanford Prison Experiment .
Sheridan played Cyclops in the 2016 film X-Men : Apocalypse , and will portray the lead character , Wade Watts , in Steven Spielberg 's adaptation of Ernest Cline 's Ready Player One , which is scheduled for a March 30 , 2018 release .